    {
      "id": "standard_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_2",
      "description": "This car is in poor condition. It has notable mechanical issues that will need to be addressed before it can be used reliably on a daily basis. The exterior shows significant wear, including scratches, dents, and other visible damage. The interior is worn with tears, stains, and general deterioration. This car is best suited for someone willing to invest in repairs.",
